msgstr "Sabaraha amanna Token éta?"

#: templates/api.html:85
msgid ""
"We are not setting the Token directly to the cookie. Instead, we are "
"generating a token based on your Token which expires in every one hour "
"then it regenerates a new token automatically. So you can say your Token "
"is super secured."
msgstr ""
"Ieu henteu nyetél Token langsung kana cookie. Sabalikna, ieu ngahasilkeun"
" token dumasar kana Token anjeun anu kadaluwarsa unggal jam teras éta "
"ngahasilkeun deui token énggal sacara otomatis. Janten anjeun tiasa "
"nyarios Token anjeun aman pisan."

